 RewriteEngine On  
 RewriteRule ^post/([a-zA-Z0-9-/]+)/([a-zA-Z0-9-/]+)$ index.php?type=post&id=$1&slug=$2
 RewriteRule ^post/([a-zA-Z0-9-/]+)/([a-zA-Z0-9-/]+)/ index.php?type=post&id=$1&slug=$2

 RewriteRule ^redirect/([a-zA-Z0-9-/]+)$ index.php?type=redirect&linkId=$1
 RewriteRule ^redirect/([a-zA-Z0-9-/]+)/ index.php?type=redirect&linkId=$1

